{"tid":391017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應福田站曾預留口岸　陳帆：政府第一天已以「一地兩檢」為目標","createTime":"2017-09-07T13:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T03:38:14.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9972336954edf85d932da3e3813067dbe3627e49","tid":391017,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回應福田站曾預留口岸　陳帆：政府第一天已以「一地兩檢」為目標<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/fan-28_L7zcz_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ffan-28_L7zcz_1200x0.png&h=0718e343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府西九高鐵站實行「一地兩檢」方案，惹起爭議。早前有報道指福田站在興建時有預留空間設置口岸，質疑政府現在為何堅持一地兩檢。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆今日回應指，「與其話我哋放棄（在福田站設置口岸），不如講係我哋選擇咗一地兩檢」，強調港府由第一天起便以「一地兩檢」為目標。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆又拿選擇終身伴侶作比喻，「你選擇咗就唔等於放棄其他吖嘛，你唔會做一個負面清單」，強調政府是從眾多方案中挑選「最好的一個」。<br />\n<br />\n深圳福田站於2015年底啟用，高鐵若由香港開出，進入內地第一站就是福田站，有建議於此站實施一地兩檢。有資料顯示福田站在興建前和興建中，都有預留樓層作「口岸設施」、「海關設置」，上月有線新聞報道則發現，現時使用該樓層的人根本不多。<br />\n<br />\n但陳帆上月於立法會上解釋不在福田站辦「一地兩檢」的原因時則稱，福田站和深圳北站早已全面運作，「你要求人哋拆卸重建，安置你香港需要，呢個我諗放喺世界任何一個地點，都係不合理同強人所難」。另外，律政司司長袁國強指，若在福田站或深圳北站實行「一地兩檢」，最大問題是乘客須於中途下車，對長者或攜帶較重行李的乘客造成不便。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%A6%8F%E7%94%B0%E7%AB%99%E6%9B%BE%E9%A0%90%E7%95%99%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8-%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9%E5%B7%B2%E4%BB%A5-%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2-%E7%82%BA%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%25A6%258F%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25B2%25B8-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B8%2586-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AA%25A2-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%25A8%2599%2F&d=5wIftwkErFWQMYrS7QDuyBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=f2b89b55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%25A6%258F%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25B2%25B8-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B8%2586-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AA%25A2-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%25A8%2599%2F&h=fabca159\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%A6%8F%E7%94%B0%E7%AB%99%E6%9B%BE%E9%A0%90%E7%95%99%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8-%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9%E5%B7%B2%E4%BB%A5-%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2-%E7%82%BA%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99/</a>"},{"pid":"01c4fb9cb567e9533376503f24cd548406c6cff7","tid":391017,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"之前俾有線定now爆大獲話講大話, 仲兜"},{"pid":"a67af8b72b9ced97b2c184c13e37de5bbf0b4e82","tid":391017,"uid":76148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"ccccccccccccccc"},{"pid":"953557fdb77be3e105216cb325f3f6c8bfb78c06","tid":391017,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a322374e265970732c4b064e15f4bf7e5c39a9","tid":391017,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前俾有線定now爆大獲話講大話, 仲兜</blockquote><br />\n有線"},{"pid":"c930b876907e3827aaf0414d040eb63c097a2897","tid":391017,"uid":21564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:53:40.000Z","msg":"佢講緊乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解咁既人做到局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/